\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-cape-town-uct-postgraduate-application\/#Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_UCT\" title=\"Applying for Financial Assistance in UCT\">Applying for Financial Assistance in UCT<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80770526\">About the University of Cape Town (UCT) Postgraduate Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80770527\">How to Apply for UCT Postgraduate Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80770528\">Documents Required for UCT Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80770529\">UCT Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80770530\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80770531\">Applying for Financial Assistance in UCT<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-university-of-cape-town-uct-postgraduate-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_University_of_Cape_Town_UCT_Postgraduate_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80770526\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751340\"><\/a>About the University of Cape Town (UCT) Postgraduate Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the University of Cape Town (UCT) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigents and International) for admission into <strong>Postgraduate programmes<\/strong> for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see they know the actual programs (Course) available for the 2024Postgraduateadmission.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-for-uct-postgraduate-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_for_UCT_Postgraduate_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80770527\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751341\"><\/a>How to Apply for UCT Postgraduate Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"http:\/\/applyonline.uct.ac.za\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Select the <strong>2024 Postgraduate Programmes<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-uct-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_UCT_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80770528\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751342\"><\/a>Documents Required for UCT Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A valid NBT Academic Literacy Test Plus report with an overall score of Upper Intermediate or above.<\/li>\n<li>A TOEFL iBT Score Report with an overall score of 88 or above, with at least 19 in Listening, 19 in Writing, 20 in Reading, and 22 in Speaking.<\/li>\n<li>A valid IELTS Academic Test Report Form with an overall score of band 6.5 or above, with at least 6.0 in each component.<\/li>\n<li>A valid PTE Academic Score Report with an overall score of 67 or above, with at least 59 in each communicative skills component.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"uct-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"UCT_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80770529\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751343\"><\/a>UCT Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee of <strong>R100<\/strong>for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of <strong>R100<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80770530\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751344\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30 September 2024 <\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-uct\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_UCT\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80770531\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751345\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in UCT<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicant can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"http:\/\/www.students.uct.ac.za\/students\/fees-funding\/postgraduate-degree-funding\/applications-requirements\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<p>International students \u2013 Click Here<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/applyonline.uct.ac.za\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Click here to Apply<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"UCT Postgraduate Application 2024 for Admission into University of Cape Town, UCT Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1183,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[66],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1181"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1181"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1181\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1181"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?p